472
00:37:57,650 --> 00:37:58,568
Sheldon.

473
00:39:02,799 --> 00:39:05,093
Bem, já passou.

474
00:39:25,154 --> 00:39:26,322
O que é isto?

475
00:39:47,552 --> 00:39:48,511
Partiu-se.

476
00:39:49,804 --> 00:39:50,722
14h18.

477
00:40:02,817 --> 00:40:04,319
Sheldon.

478
00:40:06,237 --> 00:40:07,155
Meu Deus!

